# 10. Final Service Statement

The Application Engineering Support service is designed to provide the specialized expertise required to integrate CAN into the LEAP production platform without compromising application stability, security, quality or operational readiness.

The service covers the complete application integration lifecycle—from discovery and specification review through architecture, frontend, backend, workflow orchestration, API integration, application security, testing, release readiness and hypercare.

Its primary purpose is to reduce the technical and production risks associated with introducing a significant new application workstream into an already operational platform.

